sub_title: Spatial planning expert Policy advisor strategic Spatial planner
summary:
Almost 40 years of experience as a consultant for public bodies, responsible for spatial developments. 
Consulted municipalities, regional administrations, national ministries and European institutions in the Netherlands, UK, Germany, Italy and Slovenia. Was also involved in projects in developing countries in Africa, South East Asia and South America.
Jan is committed to integrative, approaches for sustainable developments, in a comprehensive, interactice way, thereby involving relevant interrest groups.

Delivered numerous presentations on effective planning throughout Europe and guided masterclasses in Denmark and Italy

Specialties: Enhancing the effectiveness of the complex processes towards agreements in society about future development strategies.
